  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a wok or large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the finely chopped onion and minced garlic, sautéing until translucent.",
    "Stir in ground cumin and turmeric powder. Cook for about 30 seconds to release their flavors.",
    "Fold in sultanas and salt; stir well to combine all ingredients evenly.",
    "Cook the mixture for an additional 2-3 minutes or until the sultanas start to crisp up slightly.",
    "Serve hot over a bed of gluten-free rice. Garnish with fresh cilantro if desired."
